\c 9
\s UJehu ugcotshwa ukuthi abe yinkosi yakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 UElisha umprofethi wasebiza omunye wamadodana abaprofethi\x + 2.3.\x* wathi kuye: Bopha ukhalo lwakho\x + 1 Kho. 18.46.\x*, uthathe lumfuma wamafutha esandleni sakho\x + 1 Sam. 10.1.\x*, uye eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 8.28,29. 1 Kho. 22.3.\x*.
\v 2 Nxa ufika khona udinge lapho uJehu indodana kaJehoshafathi indodana kaNimshi\x + 9.14. 8.18,26. 1 Kho. 21.29. 1 Kho. 19.16. 2 Lan. 22.2. 2 Lan. 21.6. Ezra 5.1. 6.14. Zek. 1.1.\x*, ungene, umsukumise phakathi kwabafowabo\x + 9.5,11.\x*, umngenise ekamelweni elingaphakathi.
\v 3 Ubusuthatha umfuma wamafutha, uwathele ekhanda lakhe uthi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngikugcobile ube yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli. Ubusuvula umnyango, ubaleke, ungaphuzi\x + 1 Sam. 10.1\x*.
\p
\v 4 Lahamba-ke ijaha lelo, ijaha umprofethi, laya eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 5 Ekufikeni kwalo, khangela, induna zebutho zazihlezi, lathi: Ngilombiko kuwe, nduna. UJehu wasesithi: Kubani phakathi kwethu sonke? Laselisithi: Kuwe, nduna.
\v 6 Wasesukuma, wangena endlini; laselithela amafutha ekhanda lakhe, lathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Ngikugcobile ukuthi ube yinkosi phezu kwabantu beN\nd kosi\nd*, phezu kukaIsrayeli.
\v 7 Njalo uzatshaya indlu kaAhabi inkosi yakho, ukuze ngiphindisele igazi lenceku zami abaprofethi, legazi lazo zonke inceku zeN\nd kosi\nd*, esandleni sikaJezebeli\x + 1 Kho. 18.4. 21.15.\x*.
\v 8 Yonke-ke indlu kaAhabi izabhubha; njalo ngizaquma asuke kuAhabi\x + 1 Kho. 14.10. 21.21. 10.17.\x* ochamela emdulini\x + 1 Sam. 25.22.\x*, lovalelweyo lokhululekileyo koIsrayeli\x + Dute. 32.36.\x*.
\v 9 Njalo ngizakwenza indlu kaAhabi njengendlu kaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati\x + 1 Kho. 14.10. 15.29. 21.22.\x* lanjengendlu kaBahasha indodana kaAhiya\x + 1 Kho. 16.3,11.\x*.
\v 10 Lezinja zizakudla uJezebeli\x + 9.35,36. 1 Kho. 21.23.\x* esabelweni seJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*, njalo kakuyikuba lo\add m\add*ngcwabayo. Laselivula umnyango, labaleka.
\p
\v 11 Kwathi uJehu esephumele encekwini zenkosi yakhe, \add omunye\add* wathi kuye: Kulungile yini\x + 5.21.\x*? Luzeleni loluhlanya kuwe\x + 9.20. Jer. 29.26. Hos. 9.7. Joha. 10.20. Seb. 26.24.\x*? Wasesithi kuzo: Liyamazi lumuntu lenkulumo yakhe\x + 1 Kho. 18.27.\x*.
\v 12 Zasezisithi: Manga! Sitshele khathesi. Wasesithi: Ukhulume ukuthi lokuthi kimi esithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngikugcobile ube yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli.
\v 13 Zaseziphangisa, zathatha, ngulowo lalowo isembatho sakhe, zazibeka ngaphansi kwakhe engqongeni yezikhwelo\x + Mat. 21.8. Mark. 11.8.\x*, zavuthela uphondo, zathi: UJehu uyinkosi\x + 1 Kho. 1.34.\x*!
\s UJehu ubulala uJehoramu
\p
\v 14 Ngokunjalo uJehu indodana kaJehoshafathi indodana kaNimshi wamenzela ugobe uJoramu. (UJoramu wagcina-ke iRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 8.28.\x*, yena loIsrayeli wonke, ngenxa kaHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 1 Kho. 19.17.\x*;
\v 15 kodwa uJehoramu inkosi wayesebuyelele ukwelatshwa eJizereyeli ngamanxeba amaSiriya ayemtshaye wona ekulweni kwakhe loHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 8.29.\x*.) UJehu wasesithi: Aluba kuyintando yenu, kakungaphumi ophunyukileyo emzini ukuyabika lokhu eJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*.
\v 16 UJehu wasekhwela \add inqola\add*, waya eJizereyeli, ngoba uJoramu wayelele khona, loAhaziya inkosi yakoJuda wayehle ukuthi abone uJoramu\x + 8.29.\x*.
\v 17 Umlindi wayemi-ke emphotshongweni eJizereyeli, wabona ixuku likaJehu, yena esiza, wathi: Ngibona ixuku. UJehoramu wathi: Thatha umgadi webhiza u\add m\add*thume ukubahlangabeza, athi: Yikuthula yini?
\v 18 Wasehamba umgadi webhiza ukumhlangabeza, wathi: Itsho njalo inkosi: Yikuthula yini? UJehu wasesithi: Ulani lokuthula? Phendukela ngemva kwami. Umlindi wasebika esithi: Isithunywa sesifikile kibo, kodwa kasiphenduki.
\v 19 Yasithuma umgadi webhiza wesibili, wafika kibo wathi: Itsho njalo inkosi: Yikuthula yini? UJehu wasesithi: Ulani lokuthula? Phendukela ngemva kwami.
\v 20 Umlindi wasebika wathi: Usefikile kibo, kodwa kaphenduki. Lokutshayela kufanana lokutshayela kukaJehu\x + 2 Sam. 18.27.\x* indodana kaNimshi, ngoba utshayela okohlanya\x + 9.2,14.\x*.
\v 21 UJehoramu wasesithi: Bophelani. Basebebophela inqola yakhe. UJehoramu inkosi yakoIsrayeli loAhaziya inkosi yakoJuda basebephuma, ngulowo lalowo enqoleni yakhe, baphuma ukuhlangabeza uJehu\x + 2 Lan. 22.7.\x*, bamthola esiqintini sikaNabothi umJizereyeli\x + 9.25,26.\x*.
\v 22 Kwasekusithi uJehoramu ebona uJehu wathi: Yikuthula yini, Jehu? Wasesithi: Ukuthula bani, selokhu ukuwula kukaJezebeli unyoko\x + 2 Lan. 21.13. Eks. 7.11.\x* lokuthakatha kwakhe kukunengi \add kangaka\x + 2 Lan. 21.13. Eks. 7.11.\x*\add*?
\v 23 UJehoramu wasephendula izandla zakhe wabaleka, wathi kuAhaziya: Yinkohliso, Ahaziya!
\v 24 UJehu wasedonsisisa idandili, watshaya uJehoramu phakathi kweziphanga zakhe, lomtshoko waphuma enhliziyweni yakhe, wasekhothama enqoleni yakhe.
\v 25 Wasesithi kuBidikari induna yakhe\x + 7.2.\x*: Mphakamise, umphosele esiqintini sensimu kaNabothi umJizereyeli; ngoba khumbula mina lawe sigade sobabili ngemva kukaAhabi uyise\x + Isa. 21.7,9.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yamethesa\x + 1 Kho. 21.29.\x* lumthwalo\x + Isa. 13.1. 15.1. 21.1. Jer. 23.33. Zek. 9.1. Mal. 1.1.\x*:
\v 26 Ngibonile isibili izolo igazi likaNabothi legazi lamadodana akhe, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngizaphindisela kuwe kulesisiqinti, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*. Ngakho-ke mphakamise umphosele kulesisiqinti, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 21.29.\x*\nd*.
\s UJehu ubulala uAhaziya
\p
\v 27 UAhaziya inkosi yakoJuda esebonile lokhu wabaleka, ngendlela yendlu yesivande. UJehu wasexotshana laye, wathi: Mtshayeni laye enqoleni, emqansweni weGuri\x + 2 Lan. 22.9. Josh. 17.11.\x* elingaseIbileyamu\x + 2 Lan. 22.9. Josh. 17.11.\x*. Wasebalekela eMegido, wafela khona.
\v 28 Inceku zakhe zasezimthwala zamusa eJerusalema, zamngcwaba engcwabeni lakhe kuboyise emzini kaDavida\x + 23.30. 14.20.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lanye kaJoramu indodana kaAhabi, uAhaziya waba yinkosi phezu kukaJuda.
\s Ukubulawa kukaJezebeli
\p
\v 30 UJehu esefikile eJizereyeli, uJezebeli wa\add ku\add*zwa. Wasecomba amehlo akhe, wacecisa ikhanda lakhe\x + Jer. 4.30. Hez. 23.40.\x*, walunguza ngewindi\x + 2 Sam. 6.16.\x*.
\v 31 Lapho-ke uJehu engena esangweni, wasesithi: Yikuthula yini, Zimri, mbulali wenkosi yakho\x + 1 Kho. 16.9-20.\x*?
\v 32 Wasephakamisela ubuso bakhe ewindini, wathi: Ngubani ongakimi? Ngubani? Kwasekulunguza kuye abathenwa ababili, abathathu.
\v 33 Wasesithi: Mphoseleni phansi. Basebemphosela phansi; l\add elinye\add* legazi lakhe lachaphakela emdulini lemabhizeni; wasemnyathelela phansi.
\v 34 Wasengena wadla wanatha, wathi: Ake libone lo umqalekiswakazi limngcwabe, ngoba uyindodakazi yenkosi\x + 1 Kho. 16.31.\x*.
\v 35 Basebesiyamngcwaba, kodwa kabaficanga lutho olwakhe ngaphandle kokhakhayi lenyawo lempama zezandla.
\v 36 Ngakho babuyela bamtshela; wasesithi: Leli yilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma ngesandla senceku yayo uElija umTishibi lisithi: Esiqintini seJizereyeli izinja zizakudla inyama kaJezebeli\x + 9.26. 1 Kho. 21.23.\x*;
\v 37 lesidumbu sikaJezebeli sizakuba njengomquba ebusweni bomhlabathi esiqintini seJizereyeli, ukuze bangathi: Lo nguJezebeli\x + Hlab. 83.10. Jer. 8.2. 9.22. 16.4. 25.33.\x*.